Installs mycelium.sh to PREFIX/bin (default ~/.local/bin), works from a local checkout or from stdin/curl-style execution, and keeps the runtime artifact to one file. REPO_BASE is overridable so test/test.sh can exercise the stdin path without needing the repo to be public.
